1
00:00:20,800 --> 00:00:23,410
♪The autumn wind slips in,
never asking when I'll return♪

2
00:00:24,480 --> 00:00:27,170
♪Before the mirror,
I comb my hair, lips parted just so♪

3
00:00:28,270 --> 00:00:30,670
♪An old melody plays faintly,
perhaps the answer to this life♪

4
00:00:30,670 --> 00:00:33,780
♪If fate leaves any trace at all♪

5
00:00:35,700 --> 00:00:38,160
♪Wild geese disappear in the woods,
flowers wither at dusk♪

6
00:00:38,810 --> 00:00:41,780
♪How cruel the moonlight flooding
the empty tower, wine growing cold♪

7
00:00:42,140 --> 00:00:44,530
♪Long dreams and night rain
tearing through the heart of Luoyang♪

8
00:00:44,530 --> 00:00:48,380
♪Who still rides forth
to keep a vow long left behind?♪

9
00:00:49,480 --> 00:00:51,410
♪Paint the love and the hate♪

10
00:00:52,100 --> 00:00:55,040
♪With gentle strokes of ink,
like a lone wild goose flying far away♪

11
00:00:55,810 --> 00:00:57,960
♪Frost and snow to sketch memories,
drawn taut like a bow♪

12
00:00:57,960 --> 00:00:59,550
♪One arrow dyed in deepest red♪

13
00:00:59,550 --> 00:01:03,230
♪The bitter chill within my heart♪

14
00:01:03,890 --> 00:01:06,520
♪The sorrow falling between your brows♪

15
00:01:06,520 --> 00:01:08,300
♪Scalding memories lodged in my throat♪

16
00:01:08,300 --> 00:01:11,290
♪Burning away the warmth we once shared♪

17
00:01:11,290 --> 00:01:13,800
♪I would fade away
with the candle's shadow♪

18
00:01:13,800 --> 00:01:15,700
♪Sever the ties and stay behind alone♪

19
00:01:15,700 --> 00:01:18,340
♪Let you go♪

20
00:01:18,550 --> 00:01:21,240
♪Your sorrow lingers as you glance back♪

21
00:01:21,240 --> 00:01:23,150
♪This longing has already worn me thin♪

22
00:01:23,150 --> 00:01:26,460
♪We once vowed to grow old together♪

23
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:29,050
♪But if fate bears no guilt, then why♪

24
00:01:29,050 --> 00:01:33,460
♪Does it play this song of tears
for me alone?♪

25
00:01:34,340 --> 00:01:39,580
=Destiny of Love=
(Adapted from Lin Nan's novel, Destiny of Love.)

26
00:01:39,630 --> 00:01:42,400
=Episode 2=

27
00:01:45,700 --> 00:01:46,830
Your Highness, I was wrong.

28
00:01:46,830 --> 00:01:47,940
Can you please spare me?

29
00:01:48,270 --> 00:01:49,550
There are still three days left.

30
00:01:49,750 --> 00:01:51,990
I promise, you won't get married, okay?

31
00:01:52,580 --> 00:01:53,140
What?

32
00:01:53,688 --> 00:01:55,244
What nonsense are you talking about?

33
00:01:55,550 --> 00:01:56,630
In Xilin,

34
00:01:56,750 --> 00:01:58,300
if you don't get married before you die,

35
00:01:58,340 --> 00:01:59,860
you'll become a lonely ghost.

36
00:02:01,910 --> 00:02:03,470
Your Highness, that's not what I meant.

37
00:02:03,550 --> 00:02:05,190
Then what do you mean?

38
00:02:05,940 --> 00:02:07,140
I mean...

39
00:02:08,140 --> 00:02:09,670
Look.

40
00:02:10,270 --> 00:02:11,270
If you kill me,

41
00:02:11,550 --> 00:02:12,700
you'll only get a corpse.

42
00:02:13,140 --> 00:02:14,180
But if you let me go,

43
00:02:14,420 --> 00:02:15,390
what if I succeed?

44
00:02:16,020 --> 00:02:17,580
More friends, more paths to survival.

45
00:02:18,740 --> 00:02:20,390
Your Highness, I know,

46
00:02:20,550 --> 00:02:22,300
you're determined
not to marry Prince Jin.

47
00:02:22,888 --> 00:02:23,644
Don't worry.

48
00:02:23,777 --> 00:02:26,066
I, Qiao Manman,
will definitely help you with this.

49
00:02:26,990 --> 00:02:28,070
Just give me a chance,

50
00:02:29,230 --> 00:02:30,020
and I promise

51
00:02:30,390 --> 00:02:32,460
to go through fire and water

52
00:02:32,488 --> 00:02:33,866
to help you complete this task.

53
00:02:33,950 --> 00:02:34,460
Fine.

54
00:02:36,020 --> 00:02:37,580
I'll give you another chance.

55
00:02:40,300 --> 00:02:41,390
Originally,

56
00:02:41,580 --> 00:02:43,420
I was going to use 100,000 taels of gold

57
00:02:43,580 --> 00:02:44,580
as hush money.

58
00:02:45,022 --> 00:02:45,740
Not killing you.

59
00:02:47,900 --> 00:02:48,860
100,000 taels of gold.

60
00:02:49,670 --> 00:02:50,390
Hush money?

61
00:02:50,830 --> 00:02:51,580
Yuetao,

62
00:02:51,888 --> 00:02:52,700
see the guest out.

63
00:02:52,830 --> 00:02:53,460
Alright.

64
00:02:53,700 --> 00:02:55,390
Ms. Qiao, please get up.

65
00:02:55,622 --> 00:02:57,140
Your Highness, 100,000 taels of gold.

66
00:02:57,140 --> 00:02:59,050
Why don't you give me 10,000
as a deposit first?

67
00:03:00,580 --> 00:03:01,180
Farewell.

68
00:03:07,733 --> 00:03:08,444
Your Highness.

69
00:03:15,377 --> 00:03:16,169
Your Highness.

70
00:03:16,170 --> 00:03:17,900
Isn't this the fish
you sent to His Majesty

71
00:03:17,911 --> 00:03:18,644
a few days ago?

72
00:03:18,700 --> 00:03:19,070
Why...

73
00:03:19,460 --> 00:03:20,460
Father probably thought

74
00:03:20,933 --> 00:03:22,460
this fish wasn't a valuable species,

75
00:03:23,900 --> 00:03:24,950
so he returned it.

76
00:03:26,044 --> 00:03:27,070
How could His Majesty...

77
00:03:27,830 --> 00:03:30,860
Recently, Prince Jin casually drew
a painting and sent it into the palace,

78
00:03:31,390 --> 00:03:32,270
and he treasured it.

79
00:03:33,300 --> 00:03:35,070
You painstakingly
searched for this fish.

80
00:03:36,300 --> 00:03:37,270
Prince Jin is my brother.

81
00:03:38,950 --> 00:03:41,230
It's only natural for my father

82
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:42,733
to care for his disabled son.

83
00:03:46,888 --> 00:03:48,230
It thought it was valuable,

84
00:03:49,270 --> 00:03:50,180
but in the end,

85
00:03:51,700 --> 00:03:52,830
it was not welcomed.

86
00:03:59,990 --> 00:04:01,550
We always had to find a way to live.

87
00:04:09,498 --> 00:04:13,650
(Respect Teaching and Diligent Learning)

88
00:04:14,390 --> 00:04:15,580
What did you do last night?

89
00:04:15,933 --> 00:04:17,550
I sketched a portrait of the teacher.

90
00:04:19,820 --> 00:04:21,380
Sit properly, and put it away quickly.

91
00:04:34,710 --> 00:04:35,180
Stand up.

92
00:04:39,670 --> 00:04:41,380
Good day, Teacher Ji Mo.

93
00:04:43,555 --> 00:04:44,470
Good day, students.

94
00:04:45,030 --> 00:04:45,500
Please sit.

95
00:05:01,150 --> 00:05:02,800
Today, we are going to learn

96
00:05:03,350 --> 00:05:05,380
"The Analects".

97
00:05:22,670 --> 00:05:23,350
Students!

98
00:05:24,350 --> 00:05:26,860
You shall not violate
the rules of the academy.

99
00:05:27,380 --> 00:05:28,910
What rules?

100
00:05:29,380 --> 00:05:31,550
The desk and the podium

101
00:05:32,180 --> 00:05:34,790
must be kept 3 meters apart.

102
00:05:36,060 --> 00:05:38,150
The academy is run by my family.

103
00:05:38,820 --> 00:05:40,230
My rules

104
00:05:40,244 --> 00:05:41,380
are the academy's rules.

105
00:05:42,590 --> 00:05:43,180
Alright.

106
00:05:44,500 --> 00:05:45,260
Yuanxiang,

107
00:05:45,860 --> 00:05:46,620
sit down.

108
00:05:54,300 --> 00:05:56,260
We'll continue with the class.

109
00:06:00,470 --> 00:06:01,380
No...

110
00:06:02,380 --> 00:06:03,380
(Qiao Manman,)

111
00:06:03,466 --> 00:06:05,466
(look at the mess
you've gotten me into!)

112
00:06:05,501 --> 00:06:07,800
(Everything Guild)

113
00:06:08,420 --> 00:06:09,060
Ji Mo.

114
00:06:09,790 --> 00:06:10,500
Mr. Ji.

115
00:06:11,300 --> 00:06:11,710
Mr. Ji.

116
00:06:11,790 --> 00:06:13,755
Stop shouting, I'm here.

117
00:06:14,060 --> 00:06:15,150
Where did you go?

118
00:06:15,380 --> 00:06:16,420
Where else could I go?

119
00:06:16,420 --> 00:06:17,740
There's no customer here.

120
00:06:17,740 --> 00:06:18,860
So I took a nap.

121
00:06:18,866 --> 00:06:20,500
Oh, right, I have something to tell you.

122
00:06:20,620 --> 00:06:22,060
No, you listen to me first.

123
00:06:22,260 --> 00:06:23,150
I'm in trouble.

124
00:06:23,666 --> 00:06:25,177
You've known about Pei Er's matter?

125
00:06:25,177 --> 00:06:25,977
It's not that.

126
00:06:26,422 --> 00:06:28,300
I failed to
break off the engagement.

127
00:06:28,350 --> 00:06:30,190
Prince Aliya is getting married
in three days.

128
00:06:30,260 --> 00:06:31,860
I've already promised her,

129
00:06:31,860 --> 00:06:33,260
so I can't back out now.

130
00:06:34,940 --> 00:06:35,860
No, wait.

131
00:06:37,230 --> 00:06:39,300
What did you say? Pei Er?

132
00:06:39,622 --> 00:06:40,910
What happened to Pei Er again?

133
00:06:41,350 --> 00:06:42,790
Things are truly unpredictable.

134
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:44,133
I didn't expect that Madam Pei

135
00:06:44,133 --> 00:06:45,711
would actually be interested in Pei Er.

136
00:06:46,177 --> 00:06:47,300
Now that Pei Da passed away,

137
00:06:47,422 --> 00:06:48,380
there are no obstacles.

138
00:06:49,111 --> 00:06:50,420
Not only did she take your money,

139
00:06:50,860 --> 00:06:52,620
but she also exposed your entire plan.

140
00:06:52,940 --> 00:06:53,910
I've told you.

141
00:06:53,910 --> 00:06:55,350
Don't take this order.

142
00:06:55,355 --> 00:06:56,488
But you wouldn't listen.

143
00:06:56,740 --> 00:06:57,990
What are we going to do

144
00:06:57,990 --> 00:06:59,288
when Pei Er comes looking for us?

145
00:07:02,110 --> 00:07:03,670
With a wife like this,

146
00:07:03,755 --> 00:07:05,355
no wonder Pei Da prefers to be dead.

147
00:07:06,030 --> 00:07:07,110
Then tell me,

148
00:07:07,380 --> 00:07:08,590
what should we do next?

149
00:07:08,910 --> 00:07:11,740
How about we run?

150
00:07:11,790 --> 00:07:12,350
Run?

151
00:07:13,822 --> 00:07:16,600
You're going to abandon Everything Guild
that your mother left for you?

152
00:07:19,110 --> 00:07:21,670
We can come back
when everything is settled.

153
00:07:23,133 --> 00:07:25,088
Under heaven,
everything is His Majesty's land.

154
00:07:25,088 --> 00:07:27,820
You've offended the royal families
of two countries at the same time.

155
00:07:27,820 --> 00:07:30,030
Ms. Qiao, you're truly skilled.

156
00:07:30,300 --> 00:07:32,180
Where else can we run to?

157
00:07:32,300 --> 00:07:33,350
So, what you're saying is,

158
00:07:34,222 --> 00:07:36,088
I have to take care of this anyhow,
right?

159
00:07:36,230 --> 00:07:37,230
I didn't say anything.

160
00:07:38,500 --> 00:07:39,110
Forget it.

161
00:07:39,740 --> 00:07:41,420
You're useless at critical moments.

162
00:07:41,511 --> 00:07:43,022
You're nothing compared to Ji Mo.

163
00:07:44,150 --> 00:07:45,110
Still counting on Ji Mo?

164
00:07:45,377 --> 00:07:46,844
For such a small amount of money,

165
00:07:46,860 --> 00:07:47,990
you knew he had gynophobia,

166
00:07:47,990 --> 00:07:50,230
but you still arranged for him
to teach at a girls' academy.

167
00:07:50,230 --> 00:07:51,910
He gets sick as soon as
he goes to the academy.

168
00:07:51,910 --> 00:07:52,990
He is half-dead every day.

169
00:07:53,300 --> 00:07:54,260
I think his illness

170
00:07:54,500 --> 00:07:55,470
probably can't be cured.

171
00:07:57,104 --> 00:07:59,250
(Respect Teaching and Diligent Learning)

172
00:08:03,880 --> 00:08:05,590
Teacher Ji Mo,
why are you in such a hurry?

173
00:08:05,670 --> 00:08:06,711
Where are you going?

174
00:08:07,590 --> 00:08:08,470
Teacher Ji Mo,

175
00:08:08,470 --> 00:08:09,380
where are you going?

176
00:08:10,470 --> 00:08:12,044
Teacher Ji Mo, where are you going?

177
00:08:13,420 --> 00:08:15,420
What... What are you doing?

178
00:08:15,740 --> 00:08:17,790
Class is over.
Of course, I'm heading home.

179
00:08:18,150 --> 00:08:19,300
Don't rush, Teacher Ji Mo.

180
00:08:20,380 --> 00:08:22,150
I didn't quite understand

181
00:08:22,910 --> 00:08:23,940
today's lesson.

182
00:08:25,230 --> 00:08:26,260
How about

183
00:08:26,422 --> 00:08:27,620
you explain it to me properly?

184
00:08:27,740 --> 00:08:28,470
Exactly!

185
00:08:28,740 --> 00:08:30,380
Let's do it together.

186
00:08:30,420 --> 00:08:32,230
What's wrong with explaining it again?

187
00:08:32,310 --> 00:08:34,470
Teacher Ji Mo, don't decline.

188
00:08:34,740 --> 00:08:35,990
Let's go.

189
00:08:36,020 --> 00:08:37,260
So much trouble.

190
00:08:37,350 --> 00:08:38,950
What's so scary about having a meal?

191
00:08:38,950 --> 00:08:40,260
You're going too far!

192
00:08:40,260 --> 00:08:42,070
I'll fight you!

193
00:08:42,070 --> 00:08:42,430
Run!

194
00:08:42,470 --> 00:08:43,540
Don't run!

195
00:08:43,540 --> 00:08:45,540
Stop chasing me!

196
00:08:45,780 --> 00:08:47,230
Stop chasing me!

197
00:08:48,933 --> 00:08:50,560
(Everything Guild)
That's how things are.

198
00:08:50,840 --> 00:08:53,666
Let's hear everyone's opinions
and pool our wisdom.

199
00:08:53,844 --> 00:08:55,133
Are there any good ideas?

200
00:08:55,830 --> 00:08:58,140
Well, there's a way.

201
00:08:59,110 --> 00:08:59,780
You have a way?

202
00:08:59,822 --> 00:09:00,830
You're a grown-up now.

203
00:09:00,830 --> 00:09:03,711
Still being chased by a group of
female students all over the street.

204
00:09:06,740 --> 00:09:08,470
Mr. Ji, can you stop interrupting?

205
00:09:08,660 --> 00:09:09,070
Fine.

206
00:09:09,070 --> 00:09:10,350
Hurry up and tell me.

207
00:09:11,500 --> 00:09:13,380
This matter is a bit complicated.

208
00:09:13,866 --> 00:09:15,140
Let me explain it to you first.

209
00:09:15,540 --> 00:09:17,780
This bowl represents the Xilin Kingdom.

210
00:09:20,990 --> 00:09:22,710
This bowl represents Luzhao Kingdom.

211
00:09:24,740 --> 00:09:26,310
This is Her Highness.

212
00:09:28,380 --> 00:09:29,780
This is you.

213
00:09:32,070 --> 00:09:36,466
Now they're all mixed up.

214
00:09:39,190 --> 00:09:40,350
Can you still tell

215
00:09:40,740 --> 00:09:42,860
which one is you
and which one is Her Highness?

216
00:09:42,950 --> 00:09:44,430
How can I tell?

217
00:09:47,590 --> 00:09:49,140
Ji Mo! Ji Mo!

218
00:09:51,740 --> 00:09:53,990
What does this mean?

219
00:10:06,020 --> 00:10:07,540
He is so smart.

220
00:10:08,620 --> 00:10:10,500
As long as the method is right,

221
00:10:11,230 --> 00:10:12,620
I can secretly switch her.

222
00:10:12,620 --> 00:10:14,620
(Ningyuan Inn)

223
00:10:14,620 --> 00:10:19,220
(Topographic Map of Luzhao Kingdom)

224
00:10:19,222 --> 00:10:21,933
There are only three routes
from here to Prince Jin's Residence.

225
00:10:22,860 --> 00:10:23,990
I will find a way

226
00:10:24,500 --> 00:10:25,710
to block

227
00:10:25,880 --> 00:10:27,688
(Topographic Map of Luzhao Kingdom, Inn)
the other two routes.

228
00:10:29,260 --> 00:10:29,830
Hurry up!

229
00:10:30,990 --> 00:10:33,380
Three, two, one. Start crying.

230
00:10:34,230 --> 00:10:34,620
Let's go.

231
00:10:36,620 --> 00:10:37,660
(Royal weddings)

232
00:10:37,755 --> 00:10:39,977
(emphasize auspicious times
and auspicious locations.)

233
00:10:40,830 --> 00:10:42,020
According to my arrangement,

234
00:10:42,470 --> 00:10:44,260
they will definitely take this path.

235
00:10:44,740 --> 00:10:46,970
(Topographic Map of Luzhao Kingdom)
The path to our success.

236
00:10:46,977 --> 00:10:49,310
Once I force the wedding procession
onto this only path,

237
00:10:49,444 --> 00:10:51,830
I will prepare another palanquin
and park it beside you.

238
00:10:51,830 --> 00:10:52,540
(Tea)

239
00:10:52,540 --> 00:10:53,110
(Then,)

240
00:10:53,740 --> 00:10:55,830
(I will find someone to create chaos.)

241
00:10:56,990 --> 00:10:58,230
Old Ji is right.

242
00:10:58,620 --> 00:10:59,830
Smash the palanquin!

243
00:11:00,230 --> 00:11:00,830
Yes!

244
00:11:01,470 --> 00:11:03,540
Robbery! Run!

245
00:11:04,190 --> 00:11:04,740
Your Highness.

246
00:11:05,688 --> 00:11:06,422
Your Highness.

247
00:11:06,622 --> 00:11:08,044
You'll get out of the palanquin

248
00:11:08,140 --> 00:11:09,660
and get into the one I prepared.

249
00:11:10,020 --> 00:11:10,620
Then,

250
00:11:11,110 --> 00:11:13,020
you can go far away.

251
00:11:13,660 --> 00:11:14,430
Far,

252
00:11:14,710 --> 00:11:16,470
far away.

253
00:11:16,780 --> 00:11:17,900
Far? You wish!

254
00:11:18,044 --> 00:11:19,590
When they reach Prince Jin's Residence,

255
00:11:19,711 --> 00:11:21,555
there's no bride
getting out of the palanquin.

256
00:11:21,710 --> 00:11:22,470
Then we're exposed!

257
00:11:22,590 --> 00:11:23,860
Who said there's no bride?

258
00:11:24,710 --> 00:11:26,140
We are switching.

259
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:28,540
The original bride is not there,

260
00:11:28,688 --> 00:11:30,911
we'll have to substitute
with a new bride.

261
00:11:31,511 --> 00:11:34,155
So, Yuetao, you are the new bride.

262
00:11:34,340 --> 00:11:36,740
I will put on the wedding dress
and wait for you on that road.

263
00:11:36,740 --> 00:11:38,500
Your Highness, you get into
the palanquin and leave.

264
00:11:38,500 --> 00:11:39,622
We'll see how the chaos goes,

265
00:11:39,900 --> 00:11:41,590
and we shall have a short moment.

266
00:11:42,110 --> 00:11:43,830
Yuetao, you'll put on my wedding dress

267
00:11:43,955 --> 00:11:45,020
and get into the palanquin.

268
00:11:45,260 --> 00:11:47,830
And I will disguise myself
as someone creating chaos and escape.

269
00:11:49,020 --> 00:11:51,710
And, Yuetao, you won't have
to worry about not getting married.

270
00:11:51,755 --> 00:11:53,310
And you'll marry a big shot.

271
00:11:53,310 --> 00:11:55,110
This method might work.

272
00:11:55,900 --> 00:11:58,260
But Prince Jin saw you previously.

273
00:11:59,380 --> 00:12:00,430
Don't worry.

274
00:12:00,577 --> 00:12:01,900
I was employed by Your Highness

275
00:12:01,900 --> 00:12:03,620
to cancel the engagement.

276
00:12:04,288 --> 00:12:06,549
If Yuetao can't make it
at the Prince Jin's Residence,

277
00:12:06,550 --> 00:12:08,530
