280
00:12:11,350 --> 00:12:13,230
If anything happens
on your way back home...

281
00:12:15,540 --> 00:12:17,900
You don't have to return
to Luzhao Kingdom again.

282
00:12:20,430 --> 00:12:21,140
Ladies,

283
00:12:22,350 --> 00:12:24,140
is my plan perfect?

284
00:12:25,500 --> 00:12:26,230
Ms. Qiao,

285
00:12:27,020 --> 00:12:28,620
if I manage to escape this time,

286
00:12:28,666 --> 00:12:30,760
