294
00:13:04,711 --> 00:13:05,590
Yuetao, stop talking.

295
00:13:05,860 --> 00:13:06,900
I'm already nervous.

296
00:13:07,422 --> 00:13:08,590
We've already come this far,

297
00:13:08,900 --> 00:13:09,990
so we have to believe her.

298
00:13:10,430 --> 00:13:11,230
Okay.

299
00:13:12,350 --> 00:13:13,540
Yuetao, hurry and get down.

300
00:13:13,555 --> 00:13:14,800
