310
00:13:32,380 --> 00:13:33,070
Danger?

311
00:13:33,470 --> 00:13:34,590
How can there be danger?

312
00:13:34,780 --> 00:13:35,500
Listen,

313
00:13:35,555 --> 00:13:36,900
they definitely won't take action.

314
00:13:37,500 --> 00:13:38,110
If they do,

315
00:13:38,470 --> 00:13:39,140
you run.

316
00:13:39,620 --> 00:13:40,620
Okay?

317
00:13:40,950 --> 00:13:42,070
You look energetic.

318
00:13:42,470 --> 00:13:44,140
Congratulations, Prince Jin.

319
00:13:44,540 --> 00:13:45,500
Congratulations.

320
00:13:45,500 --> 00:13:46,110
Thank you.

321
00:13:46,111 --> 00:13:47,311
Congratulations, Prince Jin.

322
00:13:47,333 --> 00:13:48,777
- Congratulations.
- Thanks.

323
00:13:50,800 --> 00:13:51,310
Prince Jin,

324
00:13:51,710 --> 00:13:53,310
the original wedding route is blocked.

325
00:13:54,590 --> 00:13:56,620
I knew it.
Make sure to keep Her Highness safe.

326
00:13:56,666 --> 00:13:59,044
Someone will try to harm Her Highness
on her way here.

327
00:13:59,470 --> 00:14:01,380
Get to Her Highness now.

328
00:14:02,310 --> 00:14:03,620
If anything happens,

329
00:14:04,620 --> 00:14:05,620
kill them.

330
00:14:06,110 --> 00:14:06,540
Yes.

331
00:14:11,911 --> 00:14:14,500
Thank you. Come to Everything Guild
