337
00:14:33,260 --> 00:14:33,660
Yuetao.

338
00:14:33,830 --> 00:14:34,830
Where are we now?

339
00:14:34,866 --> 00:14:36,911
Your Highness,
the tea stall is right in front.

340
00:14:44,140 --> 00:14:44,900
Stop.

341
00:14:45,660 --> 00:14:46,350
Stop.

342
00:14:53,380 --> 00:14:54,020
What is it?

343
00:14:54,210 --> 00:14:56,100
Her Highness is thirsty.
