351
00:15:15,190 --> 00:15:16,500
Everything is under my control.

352
00:15:22,470 --> 00:15:23,660
Old Ji is so unreliable.

353
00:15:23,822 --> 00:15:25,333
Why aren't the people he sent here yet?

354
00:15:25,500 --> 00:15:27,350
Long live Your Majesty!

355
00:15:27,350 --> 00:15:28,900
Long live Father!

356
00:15:29,190 --> 00:15:29,780
Rise.

357
00:15:30,310 --> 00:15:31,430
Thank you, Your Majesty.

358
00:15:31,430 --> 00:15:32,310
Thank you, Father.

359
00:15:32,620 --> 00:15:34,590
Everyone, today is not a court session.

360
00:15:34,900 --> 00:15:36,140
It's Jin's wedding day.

361
00:15:36,660 --> 00:15:37,900
Please be my guest.

362
00:15:38,380 --> 00:15:39,540
Thank you, Your Majesty.

363
00:15:42,860 --> 00:15:43,350
Prince Jin.

364
00:15:43,860 --> 00:15:45,310
Why do you look sad?

365
00:15:45,830 --> 00:15:47,310
Today is your wedding day.

366
00:15:47,830 --> 00:15:50,070
Is there anything unsatisfactory

367
00:15:50,311 --> 00:15:51,860
about this marriage arranged by Yunnuo?

368
00:15:52,260 --> 00:15:54,020
Father, everything is perfect.

369
00:16:00,266 --> 00:16:01,644
This is a gift from your mother

370
00:16:01,950 --> 00:16:03,070
