through life.

374
00:16:59,950 --> 00:17:00,540
Mother!

375
00:17:01,260 --> 00:17:02,500
Go away.

376
00:17:07,150 --> 00:17:08,390
Mother!

377
00:17:15,190 --> 00:17:16,300
Mother!

378
00:17:18,670 --> 00:17:19,060
Jin!

379
00:17:19,740 --> 00:17:20,390
Jin!

380
00:17:21,020 --> 00:17:21,740
Jin!

381
00:17:23,230 --> 00:17:24,230
Jin!

382
00:17:27,630 --> 00:17:27,990
Jin!

383
00:17:31,780 --> 00:17:32,470
Jin!

384
00:17:35,260 --> 00:17:36,710
Jin!

385
00:17:45,580 --> 00:17:46,580
Mother's skill

386
00:17:47,470 --> 00:17:48,230
is incredible.

387
00:17:51,630 --> 00:17:52,060
Father.

388
00:17:53,340 --> 00:17:54,470
Please rest in the main hall.

389
00:17:55,670 --> 00:17:56,100
Cheer up.

390
00:18:13,540 --> 00:18:14,740
