391
00:18:15,150 --> 00:18:16,390
Smash the palanquin!

392
00:18:16,670 --> 00:18:17,100
Yes!

393
00:18:18,200 --> 00:18:19,866
Someone is trying to snatch the bride!

394
00:18:19,866 --> 00:18:21,710
Someone is trying to snatch the bride!
Robbery!

395
00:18:22,540 --> 00:18:23,150
Robbery!

396
00:18:23,150 --> 00:18:24,377
Someone is snatching the bride!

397
00:18:28,666 --> 00:18:30,430
Do you know whose palanquin is this?

398
00:18:30,710 --> 00:18:31,430
How dare you.

399
00:18:31,580 --> 00:18:32,540
Who cares!

400
00:18:32,740 --> 00:18:33,910
Everyone, grab your weapons!

401
00:18:38,540 --> 00:18:39,340
Hurry up!

402
00:18:39,630 --> 00:18:41,430
Take the clothes. Run quickly!

403
00:18:41,670 --> 00:18:42,500
Ms. Qiao...

404
00:18:44,288 --> 00:18:46,155
I guess there's a misunderstanding.

405
00:18:46,733 --> 00:18:48,740
We'll settle the score
with that girl another day.

406
00:18:48,740 --> 00:18:49,060
Run.

407
00:18:49,100 --> 00:18:50,190
Quick! Go!

408
00:18:52,630 --> 00:18:53,020
Let's go.

409
00:18:54,577 --> 00:18:56,133
Hurry up and get ready to leave.

410
00:18:56,190 --> 00:18:57,533
We can't miss the auspicious time.

411
00:18:58,300 --> 00:18:59,260
Hu Ersa is here.

412
00:19:01,580 --> 00:19:03,260
Ms. Qiao, is this part of your plan?

413
00:19:04,044 --> 00:19:06,222
No. I didn't expect Pei Er
to be such a coward.

414
00:19:06,288 --> 00:19:07,822
He ran before the fight even started.

415
00:19:07,950 --> 00:19:09,500
Exactly. Thanks to the General.

416
00:19:11,470 --> 00:19:12,780
Do something!

417
00:19:12,910 --> 00:19:14,260
I'm thinking.

418
00:19:15,430 --> 00:19:15,910
Again!

419
00:19:17,950 --> 00:19:18,260
Run.

420
00:19:19,390 --> 00:19:20,230
Run.

421
00:19:23,800 --> 00:19:24,910
Are these your people too?

422
00:19:27,340 --> 00:19:27,820
Yes.

423
00:19:28,733 --> 00:19:29,540
These are my people.

424
00:19:34,933 --> 00:19:36,260
How can there be two brides?

425
00:19:36,844 --> 00:19:38,020
Are these your people too?

426
00:19:40,488 --> 00:19:41,466
Kill them both.

427
00:19:55,666 --> 00:19:56,780
Your Highness, are you okay?

428
00:19:57,340 --> 00:19:58,820
Your Highness, run...

429
00:19:58,820 --> 00:19:59,230
Run.

430
00:19:59,300 --> 00:19:59,870
Ms. Qiao.

431
00:20:00,340 --> 00:20:01,260
Thank you so much.

432
00:20:01,260 --> 00:20:02,950
I will definitely
repay you in the future.

433
00:20:04,100 --> 00:20:05,190
Yuetao, take care.

434
00:20:05,670 --> 00:20:06,630
Your Highness, run!

435
00:20:19,300 --> 00:20:19,950
Ms. Qiao.

436
00:20:20,950 --> 00:20:21,670
Ms. Qiao.

437
00:20:28,155 --> 00:20:29,288
Protect Her Highness!

438
00:20:52,470 --> 00:20:53,100
Ms. Qiao.

439
00:20:53,100 --> 00:20:54,910
Quickly help me
to the carriage and change.

440
00:20:55,244 --> 00:20:56,020
Let's get changed.

441
00:21:30,711 --> 00:21:31,630
Protect Her Highness!

442
00:21:31,910 --> 00:21:32,230
Yes!

443
00:21:33,190 --> 00:21:33,540
Hurry up!

444
00:21:46,020 --> 00:21:47,500
Ms. Qiao, get up and get changed.

445
00:21:47,500 --> 00:21:48,644
We're running out of time.

446
00:21:49,020 --> 00:21:50,300
Wake up!

447
00:21:50,340 --> 00:21:50,990
Aliya.

448
00:21:52,500 --> 00:21:53,820
Aliya, are you okay?

449
00:21:55,670 --> 00:21:56,150
Aliya.

450
00:22:00,300 --> 00:22:01,740
General Hu, Her Highness is okay.

451
00:22:02,377 --> 00:22:03,430
What are you doing inside?

452
00:22:04,911 --> 00:22:05,990
I'm protecting Her Highness.

453
00:22:07,020 --> 00:22:07,340
Okay.

454
00:22:08,630 --> 00:22:09,430
Thank you, Yuetao.

455
00:22:09,488 --> 00:22:10,466
Get out of the palanquin.

456
00:22:10,500 --> 00:22:11,488
We're ready to set off.

457
00:22:11,500 --> 00:22:11,780
Okay.

458
00:22:15,390 --> 00:22:16,150
What to do?

459
00:22:16,820 --> 00:22:17,540
What to do?

460
00:22:18,060 --> 00:22:18,580
What to do?

461
00:22:21,950 --> 00:22:22,430
General Hu.

462
00:22:22,577 --> 00:22:23,777
Encountering such a thing

463
00:22:23,822 --> 00:22:24,820
during a wedding day

464
00:22:25,222 --> 00:22:26,020
is inauspicious.

465
00:22:26,500 --> 00:22:28,150
Shall we return to the Inn

466
00:22:28,230 --> 00:22:28,820
to rest?

467
00:22:28,850 --> 00:22:31,422
We're not in a hurry, so choose
another day to hold the ceremony.

468
00:22:31,500 --> 00:22:32,300
Another day?

469
00:22:33,600 --> 00:22:35,470
I wonder if this is
Prince Jin's intention

470
00:22:35,740 --> 00:22:36,580
or His Majesty's.

471
00:22:37,340 --> 00:22:39,190
Are you trying to
humiliate the Xilin Kingdom?

472
00:22:40,430 --> 00:22:41,100
General Hu,

473
00:22:42,580 --> 00:22:43,340
you misunderstood.

474
00:22:44,300 --> 00:22:45,150
Well then,

475
00:22:46,910 --> 00:22:47,580
let's set off.

476
00:22:58,430 --> 00:22:58,990
Go.

477
00:23:19,864 --> 00:23:22,310
(Prince Jin's Residence)

478
00:23:26,540 --> 00:23:27,060
Ms. Qiao.

479
00:23:27,580 --> 00:23:28,430
Ms. Qiao.

480
00:23:29,470 --> 00:23:30,630
Wake up.

481
00:23:30,740 --> 00:23:32,340
We're almost there.

482
00:23:34,892 --> 00:23:37,610
(Prince Jin's Residence)

483
00:23:41,150 --> 00:23:42,060
You're not well.

484
00:23:42,540 --> 00:23:43,340
Let me help you

485
00:23:43,355 --> 00:23:44,230
to get Her Highness.

486
00:23:45,150 --> 00:23:45,950
Thank you, Yunnuo.

487
00:24:37,667 --> 00:24:40,824
♪It's destined that we cannot be close♪

488
00:24:41,347 --> 00:24:44,723
♪Loving you is a secret♪

489
00:24:45,027 --> 00:24:47,646
♪Afraid of disturbing you
and then you'd distance yourself♪

490
00:24:47,753 --> 00:24:50,726
♪Endlessly♪

491
00:24:52,046 --> 00:24:55,741
♪How I wish I could dive into the sea♪

492
00:24:55,858 --> 00:24:58,473
♪And gently rest♪

493
00:24:58,575 --> 00:25:05,329
♪Is it to soothe the reason
for your heart's pain♪

494
00:25:16,540 --> 00:25:17,990
Finally, I got rid of those people.

495
00:25:20,911 --> 00:25:23,340
I didn't expect Ms.Qiao
to be so brave and resourceful.

496
00:25:24,060 --> 00:25:25,390
I finally escaped.

497
00:25:27,430 --> 00:25:29,190
Why isn't Manman here yet?

498
00:25:31,910 --> 00:25:33,020
According to the plan,

499
00:25:33,580 --> 00:25:34,780
she should be here.

500
00:25:42,150 --> 00:25:43,150
I wonder

501
00:25:43,580 --> 00:25:45,780
how are Yuetao and Ms. Qiao now.

502
00:25:46,844 --> 00:25:48,020
Are you talking about Manman?

503
00:25:55,060 --> 00:25:55,780
Buddy!

504
00:25:56,780 --> 00:25:57,260
Buddy!

505
00:25:57,670 --> 00:25:58,870
Buddy, wake up.

506
00:25:59,260 --> 00:26:00,020
Buddy!

507
00:26:00,820 --> 00:26:02,910
Help!

508
00:26:03,710 --> 00:26:05,910
Help!

509
00:26:08,820 --> 00:26:09,500
You're awake.

510
00:26:11,870 --> 00:26:12,780
Buddy, you're awake.

511
00:26:13,710 --> 00:26:14,670
