512
00:26:14,820 --> 00:26:15,820
Who are you?

513
00:26:15,844 --> 00:26:17,222
I'm Ji Mo, from Everything Guild.

514
00:26:17,300 --> 00:26:18,580
Aren't you talking about Manman?

515
00:26:19,390 --> 00:26:20,230
Manman?

516
00:26:21,630 --> 00:26:23,670
Who's that?

517
00:26:24,870 --> 00:26:25,910
Buddy!

518
00:26:45,622 --> 00:26:47,540
(The aftereffect of
Xilin Kingdom's drug)

519
00:26:48,710 --> 00:26:50,670
(is so strong.)

520
00:27:20,190 --> 00:27:20,990
(Prince Jin?)

521
00:27:21,630 --> 00:27:22,190
(Oh no!)

522
00:27:33,430 --> 00:27:35,022
Your Highness, what are you doing?

523
00:27:40,820 --> 00:27:42,470
To drink nuptial wine.

524
00:27:43,020 --> 00:27:44,230
After that,

525
00:27:44,670 --> 00:27:47,190
we'll get undressed and go to bed.

526
00:27:48,670 --> 00:27:50,230
I'm having some trouble with my legs.

527
00:27:50,500 --> 00:27:51,430
Can you...

528
00:27:51,580 --> 00:27:52,630
No.

529
00:27:52,777 --> 00:27:54,709
I haven't even said
what I'm going to do.

530
00:27:54,710 --> 00:27:55,500
See no evil,

531
00:27:55,540 --> 00:27:56,060
hear no evil,

532
00:27:56,060 --> 00:27:56,780
