533
00:27:57,230 --> 00:27:57,630
Evil?

534
00:27:58,390 --> 00:27:58,870
Um...

535
00:28:00,020 --> 00:28:01,060
Your Highness.

536
00:28:01,470 --> 00:28:03,060
