539
00:28:11,822 --> 00:28:13,260
(I've been out since I was seven.)

540
00:28:13,600 --> 00:28:15,109
(I wouldn't boast about other things,)

541
00:28:15,110 --> 00:28:17,644
(but I've never been afraid of anyone
when it comes to drinking.)

542
00:28:17,950 --> 00:28:19,150
(As long as I put you down,)

543
00:28:19,470 --> 00:28:21,100
(everything will be easy.)

544
00:28:21,120 --> 00:28:23,250
(Everything Guild)

545
00:28:23,820 --> 00:28:25,260
Dad!

546
00:28:25,430 --> 00:28:26,150
Help me.

547
00:28:26,340 --> 00:28:27,740
