551
00:28:31,430 --> 00:28:32,580
Where did Qiao Manman go?

552
00:28:32,580 --> 00:28:33,630
I have no idea.

553
00:28:33,630 --> 00:28:34,730
Don't worry about it for now.

554
00:28:34,733 --> 00:28:35,720
Dad, take a look at him.

555
00:28:35,990 --> 00:28:36,470
This...

556
00:28:36,710 --> 00:28:38,020
Put him down.

557
00:28:38,020 --> 00:28:38,670
Over here.

558
00:28:41,780 --> 00:28:43,260
I'm holding him.

559
00:28:43,300 --> 00:28:44,670
Let go.

560
00:28:48,870 --> 00:28:49,580
Amazing.

561
00:28:50,670 --> 00:28:52,260
Your gynophobia is cured.

562
00:28:52,555 --> 00:28:53,950
You actually carried a woman back.

563
00:28:54,540 --> 00:28:55,820
Woman?

564
00:29:05,430 --> 00:29:06,020
Son.

565
00:29:11,950 --> 00:29:12,580
Aliya.

566
00:29:14,540 --> 00:29:15,500
Oh my God.

567
00:29:17,340 --> 00:29:18,990
This isn't bringing a woman back.

568
00:29:19,710 --> 00:29:21,300
This is bringing back

569
00:29:21,300 --> 00:29:21,910
a Princess!

570
00:29:22,910 --> 00:29:23,950
If you're here,

571
00:29:24,870 --> 00:29:25,780
then where is Manman?

572
00:29:50,870 --> 00:29:52,500
No, I can't drink anymore.

573
00:29:52,580 --> 00:29:53,630
I can't drink anymore.

574
00:30:04,670 --> 00:30:05,780
Don't come over.

575
00:30:10,230 --> 00:30:11,100
Go away!

576
00:30:23,060 --> 00:30:24,060
What are you doing?

577
00:30:25,190 --> 00:30:27,580
I bought a new dagger
and I wanted to show you.

578
00:30:30,540 --> 00:30:31,710
What is wrong with you?

579
00:30:33,990 --> 00:30:35,150
You are crazy.

580
00:30:45,355 --> 00:30:47,230
Aliya, please forgive my rudeness.

581
00:30:47,870 --> 00:30:50,300
Actually, I know what you
were thinking when we met

582
00:30:50,311 --> 00:30:51,511
during the Lantern Festival.

583
00:30:51,555 --> 00:30:52,820
Neither of us intended to marry,

584
00:30:53,580 --> 00:30:55,470
but now we can only make the best of it.

585
00:30:55,910 --> 00:30:58,260
I will find a way to help you leave
when I have the chance.

586
00:30:59,266 --> 00:31:01,444
(Although he said
we'd make the best of it,)

587
00:31:01,740 --> 00:31:03,580
(he's treating me as the real princess.)

588
00:31:03,990 --> 00:31:04,910
(If I'm exposed,)

589
00:31:05,000 --> 00:31:06,577
(and he calls off the marriage,)

590
00:31:06,740 --> 00:31:08,430
(I'll be the one who got beheaded!)

591
00:31:08,870 --> 00:31:10,870
Since we must share a room now,

592
00:31:10,950 --> 00:31:13,340
please take note of the following.

593
00:31:13,870 --> 00:31:14,340
First,

594
00:31:14,910 --> 00:31:16,780
it's not my fault to be this handsome,

595
00:31:16,870 --> 00:31:19,190
but it is your fault
if you fall in love with me.

596
00:31:19,422 --> 00:31:21,088
So, please, don't fall in love with me.

597
00:31:21,260 --> 00:31:21,710
Next,

598
00:31:22,150 --> 00:31:23,820
we must have our own space

599
00:31:23,870 --> 00:31:24,933
and respect each other.

600
00:31:25,060 --> 00:31:26,639
After the maid leaves the residence,

601
00:31:26,640 --> 00:31:27,880
we'll sleep in a separate room.

602
00:31:28,150 --> 00:31:30,060
Last but not least,

603
00:31:31,600 --> 00:31:33,670
you'll sleep on the couch
and I'll sleep on the bed.

604
00:31:36,230 --> 00:31:37,500
Get up now.

605
00:31:37,500 --> 00:31:38,511
Hey!

606
00:31:38,511 --> 00:31:39,266
Aliya!

607
00:31:46,020 --> 00:31:47,500
Aliya!

608
00:31:48,100 --> 00:31:48,820
Aliya!

609
00:32:01,466 --> 00:32:02,355
Your Highness.

610
00:32:02,800 --> 00:32:05,200
I had the chance
to force Her Highness to return.

611
00:32:05,580 --> 00:32:07,060
But Jiufeng came with a team of men

612
00:32:07,540 --> 00:32:08,533
and ruined the plan.

613
00:32:09,088 --> 00:32:10,711
Please punish me, Your Highness.

614
00:32:13,950 --> 00:32:15,020
Luckily Brother

615
00:32:15,580 --> 00:32:17,150
protected Princess Aliya this time.

616
00:32:18,260 --> 00:32:20,780
Otherwise, Mother
would have made a grave mistake.

617
00:32:21,133 --> 00:32:23,311
I will send people
to investigate again tomorrow.

618
00:32:23,488 --> 00:32:24,230
She is out there.

619
00:32:24,710 --> 00:32:26,022
There's nothing you can do.

620
00:32:26,950 --> 00:32:27,710
Things happen.

621
00:32:28,390 --> 00:32:29,260
Let it be.

622
00:32:29,990 --> 00:32:30,710
I'm incompetent.

623
00:32:30,990 --> 00:32:31,990
I'll take twenty strokes

624
00:32:32,470 --> 00:32:33,190
as punishment.

625
00:32:36,300 --> 00:32:37,060
Fifty.

626
00:32:39,470 --> 00:32:39,910
Yes.

627
00:32:47,540 --> 00:32:48,870
What exactly happened

628
00:32:49,111 --> 00:32:50,733
when I asked you to escort Her Highness?

629
00:32:51,300 --> 00:32:52,300
I have no idea.

630
00:32:52,710 --> 00:32:55,266
When I arrived, there was already
a group of people in black.

631
00:32:55,540 --> 00:32:56,950
And there was someone

632
00:32:56,950 --> 00:32:57,580
as strong as me.

633
00:33:04,020 --> 00:33:05,430
They failed.

634
00:33:05,740 --> 00:33:06,950
Twice.

635
00:33:07,020 --> 00:33:08,190
The mastermind knew

636
00:33:08,540 --> 00:33:10,100
that we were prepared.

637
00:33:10,266 --> 00:33:12,155
They will not come after
us again so easily.

638
00:33:12,300 --> 00:33:13,540
It seems that for now,

639
00:33:13,870 --> 00:33:15,230
we can only wait and see.

640
00:33:18,446 --> 00:33:20,780
(Benevolent and Kind)

641
00:33:26,500 --> 00:33:27,150
No way.

642
00:33:27,910 --> 00:33:29,300
I must escape.

643
00:33:29,300 --> 00:33:31,622
Otherwise, my identity will be exposed
sooner or later.

644
00:33:39,300 --> 00:33:40,540
Who are you?

645
00:33:42,020 --> 00:33:42,990
How did you get in

646
00:33:43,190 --> 00:33:44,340
without a sound?

647
00:33:45,177 --> 00:33:46,044
Where is Yuetao?

648
00:33:47,060 --> 00:33:48,060
Yuetao.

649
00:33:48,190 --> 00:33:49,190
I'm here.

650
00:33:51,800 --> 00:33:52,955
Yes, Your Highness.

651
00:33:55,230 --> 00:33:56,340
I'm Chuncan.

652
00:33:56,340 --> 00:33:57,710
I'm the Head Maid in the palace.

653
00:33:57,777 --> 00:33:59,390
His Majesty is worried that you might

654
00:33:59,390 --> 00:34:01,000
not adapt well to
the Luzhao Kingdom.

655
00:34:01,000 --> 00:34:02,580
So he arranged for me to come here

656
00:34:02,580 --> 00:34:03,950
to help out with you.

657
00:34:07,150 --> 00:34:08,177
Head Maid?

658
00:34:09,470 --> 00:34:10,830
You may call me Madam Chuncan

659
00:34:10,950 --> 00:34:12,990
just like His Highness.

660
00:34:16,020 --> 00:34:17,660
His Highness has done showering.

661
00:34:17,990 --> 00:34:20,270
Your Highness,
you may bathe and change too.

662
00:34:34,733 --> 00:34:35,533
Madam Chuncan.

663
00:34:35,711 --> 00:34:37,879
How's the Prince Jin's Residence
on a usual day?

664
00:34:37,880 --> 00:34:39,590
How many people are there?
How many guards?

665
00:34:40,350 --> 00:34:42,660
Because of His Highness's leg problem,

666
00:34:42,950 --> 00:34:44,700
he is a very reserved person.

667
00:34:44,910 --> 00:34:45,990
So there aren't many maids

668
00:34:46,180 --> 00:34:48,180
or guards in Prince Jin's Residence.

669
00:34:49,750 --> 00:34:50,540
However,

670
00:34:50,580 --> 00:34:52,540
there was an accident
on your route yesterday.

671
00:34:53,540 --> 00:34:55,310
His Majesty is worried about the safety.

672
00:34:55,660 --> 00:34:58,390
So he added a large number of guards,
temporarily.

673
00:34:58,470 --> 00:35:00,060
(It seems escaping)

674
00:35:00,222 --> 00:35:01,950
(the Prince Jin's Residence
won't be easy.)

675
00:35:02,990 --> 00:35:04,430
Your Highness, don't worry.

676
00:35:04,990 --> 00:35:06,100
I've arranged

677
00:35:06,350 --> 00:35:08,470
everything for you in the Residence.

678
00:35:09,866 --> 00:35:12,000
You are the divine physician
of Xilin Kingdom.

679
00:35:12,020 --> 00:35:13,060
You married His Highness

680
00:35:13,060 --> 00:35:14,620
and helped to treat his legs.

681
00:35:15,580 --> 00:35:17,700
This is truly a blessing for him.

682
00:35:18,790 --> 00:35:20,830
(I don't know anything about medicine.)

683
00:35:20,990 --> 00:35:21,990
(Divine physician?)

684
00:35:22,430 --> 00:35:23,750
(Treating His Highness's legs?)

685
00:35:27,350 --> 00:35:28,750
Am I dressing up

686
00:35:29,100 --> 00:35:30,350
to meet His Majesty?

687
00:35:31,100 --> 00:35:33,830
Her Highness, His Majesty is usually
busy with his official duties.

688
00:35:33,888 --> 00:35:35,310
You can't meet him without a summons.

689
00:35:35,660 --> 00:35:37,060
After the third day of marriage,

690
00:35:37,060 --> 00:35:38,910
you can enter the palace
and meet His Majesty.

691
00:35:38,911 --> 00:35:40,580
You're now married
into the royal family,

692
00:35:40,830 --> 00:35:42,990
you should address
His Majesty as Father.

693
00:35:47,830 --> 00:35:50,100
Right, on the third day,

694
00:35:50,100 --> 00:35:52,500
General Hu Ersa
will depart for Xilin Kingdom.

695
00:35:52,688 --> 00:35:54,270
At that time, both you and His Highness

696
00:35:54,430 --> 00:35:56,020
will see him off.

697
00:35:56,311 --> 00:35:58,050
Besides the gift
prepared by His Highness,

698
00:35:58,100 --> 00:36:00,140
do you want to review

699
00:36:00,390 --> 00:36:01,470
and add some items?

700
00:36:02,620 --> 00:36:03,910
Hu Ersa...

701
00:36:05,580 --> 00:36:06,700
Three days later?

702
00:36:41,077 --> 00:36:45,437
♪The clouds stretch endlessly
across the sky♪

703
00:36:48,277 --> 00:36:52,677
♪Looking down at eyes
that gaze into the distance♪

704
00:36:54,237 --> 00:36:57,407
♪Time keeps moving on♪

705
00:36:58,027 --> 00:37:00,587
♪Whose footprints are left behind?♪

706
00:37:00,987 --> 00:37:07,447
♪It's more than
just the courage to yearn♪

707
00:37:09,077 --> 00:37:11,887
♪It's destined that we cannot be close♪

708
00:37:12,727 --> 00:37:15,807
♪Loving you is a secret♪

709
00:37:16,347 --> 00:37:19,007
♪Afraid of disturbing you
and then you'd distance yourself♪

710
00:37:19,007 --> 00:37:22,347
♪Endlessly♪

711
00:37:23,427 --> 00:37:26,877
♪How I wish I could dive into the sea♪

712
00:37:27,257 --> 00:37:29,877
♪And gently rest♪

713
00:37:29,877 --> 00:37:36,837
♪It's to soothe the reason
for your heart's pain♪

714
00:37:37,207 --> 00:37:41,487
♪If everything could overcome
all barriers and fall in love♪

715
00:37:41,837 --> 00:37:44,357
♪Even the cloud and sea
could be together♪

716
00:37:44,567 --> 00:37:47,767
♪Forget how far from shore
and how dangerous it is♪

717
00:37:48,017 --> 00:37:51,657
♪We can't see♪

718
00:37:51,867 --> 00:37:56,197
♪If distance can't tear us apart
and it's not hard to endure♪

719
00:37:56,197 --> 00:37:58,947
♪Our tears will stay together♪

720
00:37:59,197 --> 00:38:04,837
♪Don’t forget the love♪

721
00:38:06,457 --> 00:38:09,827
♪They could never have♪
